msgctxt "274	MSG"
msgid "The apprentice will get back up once more even if his Stamina reaches zero. "
msgstr "El aprendiz volverá a levantarse cuando su estamina llegue a cero. "

msgctxt "351	MSG"
msgid "Attack rate will increase after the opponent is cornered. "
msgstr "Atacará más cuando el oponente esté acorralado. "

msgctxt "410	MSG"
msgid "Attack rate will increase for 10 seconds after the fight starts. However, this Skill becomes ineffective once you get hit."
msgstr "Atacará más por los primeros 10 segundos. La habilidad quedará obsoleta si se recibe un golpe antes de esos 10 segundos."

msgctxt "533	MSG"
msgid "The apprentice's Mood determines his attack rate. There is a 70％ chance the attack rate will increase."
msgstr "Los ánimos del aprendiz determinan cuanto ataca. Hay un 70% de posibilidad de que aumente su taza de ataque."

msgctxt "638	MSG"
msgid "Abilities will be enhanced if the opponent has more Stamina than the apprentice. Abilities will decrease if the opponent has less Stamina."
msgstr "Las habilidades serán mejoradas si el oponente tiene más estamina que el aprendiz. Serán empeoradas si el oponente tiene menos estamina."

msgctxt "777	MSG"
msgid "The apprentice's Mood will improve by one level. However, his post-fight fatigue will be greater than usual."
msgstr "Los ánimos del aprendiz aumentarán un nivel. Sin embargo, su fatiga post-pelea será mayor de lo normal."

msgctxt "886	MSG"
msgid "Increases the prize purse. However, the apprentice will be more open to damage from the opponent, as he will be distracted by fan reaction."
msgstr "Aumenta el premio del torneo. Pero el aprendiz bajará sus defensas, al estar distraido por las reacciones de la multitud."

msgctxt "1026	MSG"
msgid "The apprentice's abilities increases greatly if you do not give orders during a fight. Giving orders will have the opposite effect."
msgstr "Las habilidades del aprendiz aumentarán mucho si no le das órdenes. Darle órdenes tendrá el efecto contrario."

msgctxt "1158	MSG"
msgid "The apprentice's abilities will increase when fighting in a match that he lost before. Losing the second time does not decrease his Mood."
msgstr "Las habilidades del aprendiz aumentarán cuando esté peleando en un torneo que haya perdido anteriormente. Perder una segunda vez no afectará a sus ánimos."

msgctxt "1296	MSG"
msgid "Abilities will increase overall in accordance with the Trust level the apprentice has with Saejima."
msgstr "Las habilidades aumentarán acorde al nivel de confianza que el aprendiz tenga con Saejima."

